/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scott Hanson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a [very] different approach\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"some nontraditional voices\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"expert communicators\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"their perspective\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"watch parties\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the most comprehensive whip-around show\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Gold Zone\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"company\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on Peacock we are also going to have all of these contributors, plus Leslie Jones is going to be joining us for social coverage, and she's coming the second week of the Games to bring it on home.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leslie_Ronald_Jones\", \"score\": 0.9959779475579327, \"rank\": 0.003978011815429592, \"text\": \"Leslie Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leslie_Ronald_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leslie_Ronald_Jones\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"these contributors\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"social coverage\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, of course, joining us in prime time is a man who needs no introduction, Snoop Dogg.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"prime time\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"no introduction\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His general love of the Olympics and respect for the athletes has been shining bright for months, and now here in the host city, I can not wait for you to hear about his experiences so far in Paris.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998505024932408, \"rank\": 0.00014951985791875552, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His general love\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"his experiences\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know that viewers can not wait to see his daily adventures here in Paris.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2468, \"end\": 2473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998505024932408, \"rank\": 0.00014951985791875552, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"his daily adventures\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's enough from me.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think you want to hear from two other guys, Mike Tirico and Snoop Dogg.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}, {\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two other guys\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So let us get started with your questions.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"your questions\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q.Molly, we will start with you.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years ago at the Winter Olympic Games, you made the call to have all the play-by-play and the color commentary people not go to Beijing because of issues with the Chinese government, other things too, and do it from the NBC Sports studios in Stamford, Connecticut.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8053076835413298, \"rank\": 0.2417436840072371, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2817, \"end\": 2835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9990267332091131, \"rank\": 0.0004939331374312455, \"text\": \"Chinese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9988005125095527, \"rank\": 0.0010865859931874077, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2896, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford,_Connecticut\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stamford, Connecticut\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford,_Connecticut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford,_Connecticut\"}, {\"begin\": 2896, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford,_Connecticut\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stamford, Connecticut\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford,_Connecticut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford,_Connecticut\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Winter Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"the color commentary\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"other things\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It looks like the majority of play-by-play people and color commentary people are doing the same thing again.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"play-by-play people\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"color commentary\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are some play-by-play people that will be in Paris the entire time, for gymnastics, for swimming and so forth.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998505024932408, \"rank\": 0.00014951985791875552, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some play-by-play people\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3117}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why that?\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why this move?\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Why this move\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the fact the pandemic is over, it must be easier to go to Paris rather than Beijing, why that determination?\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3235, \"end\": 3240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"s