r\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Molly, you took this role in November of 2019, and we obviously know what happened after that with COVID and delayed games and higher security around games.\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 4006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this role\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3875}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3887}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"delayed games\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"higher security\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3992}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How much more has this experience felt like maybe what you thought this job might feel like when you first took it back in 2019?\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this experience\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4040}, {\"ngram\": \"this job\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MOLLY SOLOMON: I could not be more excited about Paris, and what I love about working on the Olympics is every time you start to begin on a new city and a new four-year cycle, it's a blank slate.\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4186, \"end\": 4191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999133070264388, \"rank\": 8.670048825343275e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"MOLLY SOLOMON\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"every time\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4252}, {\"ngram\": \"a new city\", \"from\": 4275, \"to\": 4285}, {\"ngram\": \"a new four-year cycle\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4311}, {\"ngram\": \"a blank slate\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when we realized we had Paris 2024, the first thing we 