\"International stars are some of the best players in the NBA.\", \"from\": 14630, \"to\": 14690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14686, \"end\": 14689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999998847864684, \"rank\": 1.1518568603317184e-07, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"International stars\", \"from\": 14630, \"to\": 14649}, {\"ngram\": \"the best players\", \"from\": 14662, \"to\": 14678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's no surprise now that those teams have gotten deeper and better.\", \"from\": 14691, \"to\": 14759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no surprise\", \"from\": 14696, \"to\": 14707}, {\"ngram\": \"those teams\", \"from\": 14717, \"to\": 14728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe South Sudan was a wake-up call to this group, which has happened in prior exhibition runs up to Olympic Games, but it also might be eye opening to the rest of the world that the USA is not this undefeated behemoth that it was from the Dream Team days.\", \"from\": 14761, \"to\": 15018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14945, \"end\": 14948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9973744505155435, \"rank\": 0.0014903679090688007, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 15002, \"end\": 15012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.608712729241028, \"rank\": 0.6428110524931874, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"South Sudan\", \"from\": 14767, \"to\": 14778}, {\"ngram\": \"a wake-up call\", \"from\": 14783, \"to\": 14797}, {\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 14801, \"to\": 14811}, {\"ngram\": \"prior exhibition\", \"from\": 14835, \"to\": 14851}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Games\", \"from\": 14863, \"to\": 14876}, {\"ngram\": \"eye opening\", \"from\": 14899, \"to\": 14910}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 14914, \"to\": 14922}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 14926, \"to\": 14935}, {\"ngram\": \"this undefeated behemoth\", \"from\": 14956, \"to\": 14980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SNOOP DOGG: Remember when the Dream Team was formed, in those days of the Olympics, there was probably two players from across the water that were in the NBA.\", \"from\": 15020, \"to\": 15178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15050, \"end\": 15060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.608712729241028, \"rank\": 0.6428110524931874, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 15174, \"end\": 15177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999998847864684, \"rank\": 1.1518568603317184e-07, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SNOOP DOGG\", \"from\": 15020, \"to\": 15030}, {\"ngram\": \"those days\", \"from\": 15076, \"to\": 15086}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 15090, \"to\": 15102}, {\"ngram\": \"two players\", \"from\": 15123, \"to\": 15134}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 15147, \"to\": 15156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now there is 40-something players in the NBA as we speak.\", \"from\": 15179, \"to\": 15236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15220, \"end\": 15223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999998847864684, \"rank\": 1.1518568603317184e-07, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"40-something players\", \"from\": 15192, \"to\": 15212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So what that means is there is more competition coming from over the water, there is more players that are All-Stars that are from different countries.\", \"from\": 15237, \"to\": 15388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more competition\", \"from\": 15268, \"to\": 15284}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 15302, \"to\": 15311}, {\"ngram\": \"more players\", \"from\": 15322, \"to\": 15334}, {\"ngram\": \"All-Stars\", \"from\": 15344, \"to\": 15353}, {\"ngram\": \"different countries\", \"from\": 15368, \"to\": 15387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you get three or four of them on one team, then you can have the access of actually knocking off an American team because you have got All-Stars on your team.\", \"from\": 15389, \"to\": 15552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15494, \"end\": 15502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9277322229627972, \"rank\": 0.07529053862745758, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one team\", \"from\": 15427, \"to\": 15435}, {\"ngram\": \"the access\", \"from\": 15455, \"to\": 15465}, {\"ngram\": \"All-Stars\", \"from\": 15529, \"to\": 15538}, {\"ngram\": \"your team\", \"from\": 15542, \"to\": 15551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the surface has changed as far as global approach with NBA basketball.\", \"from\": 15554, \"to\": 15627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15612, \"end\": 15615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999997469995243, \"rank\": 2.525795566159807e-07, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 15557, \"to\": 15568}, {\"ngram\": \"global approach\", \"from\": 15591, \"to\": 15606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is so many superstars that are not from America that, when you put them against America, it's sort of even because there is talent everywhere now.\", \"from\": 15628, \"to\": 15780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many superstars\", \"from\": 15637, \"to\": 15655}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 15674, \"to\": 15681}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 15714, \"to\": 15721}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 15758, \"to\": 15764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MIKE TIRICO: You are right, and we are lucky in America because the best league in a lot of those major sports is in our backyard, and the aspirational part -- that's why the Dream Team is one of the great teams in the history of any sport because not only were they terrific and dominant, they also helped open the door for the globalization of the NBA.\", \"from\": 15782, \"to\": 16136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15957, \"end\": 15967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9997830796655206, \"rank\": 0.00021696708440872408, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 16132, \"end\": 16135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.99999974699